data.text:
CAREER STATISTICS

AT GEORGIA STATE: Joins the Panther program in 2017 as a graduate transfer ... Spent four years at San Diego State.

AT SAN DIEGO STATE: Part of four straight bowl teams ... Played in 14 games in 2015 with one start (at Penn State) ... Made one catch for no gain ... Redshirted in 2013 and did not see any action in 2014 ... Named to the Mountain West Fall All-Academic team.

HIGH SCHOOL: Had 38 receptions for 708 yards and six touchdowns for Jireh Prep in Matthews, N.C. ... Originally played at Troup High School, where he was the Scholar-Athlete of the Year ... Played in the North-South All-State game ... Captained the team as a senior ... ... Also lettered three years in basketball.

PERSONAL: Full name is Christian Carthage Cumberlander ... Born Jan. 3, 1994 ... Son of Jesse and Madalyn Lee Cumberlander.
